      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no point anymore. everyone at school is just constantly talking about me, making fun of everything. i can't even walk down the hall without feeling like everyone is laughing behind my back. it's like the whole world decided i don't belong and i'm just stuck here waiting for the next thing to happen. i'm so tired of everywhere feeling so hostile.",
